@host = http://localhost:5252

# Self-contained happy path — no copy/paste. Run requests top-to-bottom in VS Code REST Client
# or Visual Studio (.http support). Allow ~2s after step 3 for background workers.

### 1. Create a tenant
# @name createTenant
POST {{host}}/api/tenants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Acme Corp",
  "rateLimitPerMinute": 100
}

###

@tenantId = {{createTenant.response.body.$.id}}

### 2. Create a routing rule for that tenant
# Maps order.created events to the Slack channel.
POST {{host}}/api/tenants/{{tenantId}}/rules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventType": "order.created",
  "channelType": "slack"
}

### 3. Ingest an event
# Event queue → routing worker → dispatch queue → delivery worker → Slack.
POST {{host}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "{{tenantId}}",
  "eventType": "order.created",
  "payload": "{\"orderId\": \"ord-001\", \"amount\": 49.99}"
}
